trans-unit.source: Maintains the collection of sub-properties of a given parent <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry"></xref>.

Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntryCollection"></xref> class using the sub-properties of the specified <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntryCollection.ParentValue*> instance.
The parent <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue"></xref> instance used for the initialization.

Gets the number of <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry"></xref> instances in this collection (typically the number of sub-properties for the parent <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue"></xref>).
An integer that specifies the number of instances in this collection.
Returns an <xref:Systems.Collections.IEnumerator> object that iterates all the <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry"></xref> instances in this collection.
An <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601> that can be used to iterate through the collection of <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry"></xref> instances.
Gets a <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry"></xref> instance with the specified name from this collection.
It is used for sub-property retrieval.
The name of the property to get.
A property entry instance with the specified name; or <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref> if it does not exist.
Gets the parent <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue"></xref> from the host infrastructure.
Returns an <xref:Systems.Collections.IEnumerator> object that iterates all of the <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry"></xref> instances in this collection.
An <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator> object that can be used to iterate through collection of <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry"></xref> instances.
